      },
      "date": "2018-11-07 21:38:46.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nPassed enforced test custom on CentOS 7.0/x86_64 uploaded by AT Release Candidate from trevis-66vm7: https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/b27faa4a-7c76-4af1-a13d-5390804a9826 ran 3 tests.",
